---
// src/pages/cafe-brentwood-tn.astro
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cafe Near Brentwood, TN | Coffee & Food | The Local Place"
  description="The Local Place Cafe in Centerville serves specialty coffee, fresh pastries, breakfast, lunch, and homemade ice cream. Just 40 minutes from Brentwood. Order online or visit us."
  keywords="cafe near Brentwood, coffee Brentwood area, breakfast Centerville, drive from Brentwood"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Cafe Near Brentwood, TN</h1>
      <p>Worth the 40-Minute Drive for Real Coffee & Fresh Food</p>
      <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" class="hero-cta">Order Online</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><span>Cafe Near Brentwood</span></li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <section class="location-intro">
      <h2>Stop By The Local Place Cafe</h2>
      <p>
        You're in Brentwood, and you want real coffee. Real pastries. Not chain store stuff. Drive 40 minutes to Centerville and find The Local Place Cafe. House-made pastries, perfectly pulled espresso, homemade ice cream. It's the kind of place where you notice a difference.
      </p>
      <p>
        Perfect weekend trip with family. Stop for breakfast on your way to somewhere else. Or make it the destination. Either way, you're getting quality.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Easy Drive from Brentwood</h3>
        <p><strong>Distance:</strong> 40 minutes south</p>
        <p><strong>Route:</strong> I-65 South → Exit onto TN-100 → Centerville</p>
        <p><strong>Parking:</strong> Free parking on Public Square</p>
        <p>
          Easy navigation. Comfortable drive. Worth it when you taste our coffee and try a fresh pastry.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Why Brentwood Visitors Choose Us</h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li>Specialty coffee pulled fresh. No burnt taste.</li>
          <li>House-made pastries daily. Croissants, muffins, cinnamon rolls.</li>
          <li>Homemade ice cream. Rotating flavors. Better than anything you can buy.</li>
          <li>Fresh lunch items. Paninis, salads, wraps made to order.</li>
          <li>Community vibe. Comfortable seating. People actually linger here.</li>
          <li>Can order ahead on Clover. Grab and go or sit and stay.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Menu Highlights</h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li><strong>Specialty Coffee:</strong> Espresso, cappuccino, latte, cold brew—all done right</li>
          <li><strong>Pastries:</strong> Croissants, cinnamon rolls, blueberry muffins, scones</li>
          <li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Sandwiches, bagels, breakfast plates</li>
          <li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Paninis, salads, wraps, soups</li>
          <li><strong>Ice Cream:</strong> Homemade, rotating flavors, seriously good</li>
          <li><strong>Smoothies:</strong> Fresh blended drinks and cold beverages</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Hours & Contact</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Monday-Friday:</strong> 6 AM - 6 PM<br />
          <strong>Saturday:</strong> 9 AM - 6 PM<br />
          <strong>Sunday:</strong> Closed
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Address:</strong> 111 South Public Square<br />
          Centerville, TN 37033<br />
          <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:(931)729-3481">(931) 729-3481</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>What Brentwood Visitors Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-cards">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"We drive out from Brentwood for brunch. The pastries are insane. Fresh. Not frozen. You can taste the difference. Now we go monthly."</p>
          <p><strong>- Lisa & Tom (Brentwood)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"Family outing from Brentwood. Kids love the ice cream, adults love the coffee and lunch. Everyone's happy. Worth the drive."</p>
          <p><strong>- The Martinez Family (Brentwood)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"We were passing through from Brentwood and stopped. Best espresso I've had in years. Now I stop here every time I'm driving that way."</p>
          <p><strong>- David (Professional)</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <h2>Questions from Brentwood Visitors</h2>
      <div class="faq-items">
        <details class="faq-item" open>
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>How long is the drive from Brentwood?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>About 40 minutes south from Brentwood. Easy drive. Take I-65 South and follow signs to Centerville. We're on Public Square.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Is it worth driving 40 minutes for coffee?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes. Real espresso, house-made pastries, homemade ice cream. Once you taste the difference, you'll understand. Plus you're getting breakfast, lunch, or ice cream—not just coffee.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I order ahead from Brentwood?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes! Use Clover to order online before you drive. Your order will be ready when you arrive. Saves time and gets you hot coffee.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What's the parking situation?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Free parking on Public Square. Easy access. Come in, grab your coffee, sit if you want, or take it back to Brentwood.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Do you have seating for groups?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes, comfortable seating. Call ahead if you're bringing a large group. We can make sure we have space for you.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .content-block {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .content-block a {
    color: #8b4513;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .content-block a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .testimonial-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .testimonial-card p:first-child {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .testimonial-card p:last-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .faq-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: var(--light-gray);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    user-select: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-question:hover {
    background: #efefef;
  }

  .toggle-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .toggle-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .testimonial-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
